{"tid":591016,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你曾經發過恐怖嘅夢係咩 ？ ［靈異/恐怖］","createTime":"2018-03-13T07:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T04:30:49.000Z","uid":116257,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a19120e16cd49b049166072d8b8e0f6b67a01a91","tid":591016,"uid":116257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:15:13.000Z","msg":"問朋友借ac嚟討論吓... （可能有啲長）<br />\n<br />\n其實自己遇到嘅恐怖嘢好多，尤其是訓覺嗰陣，唔肯定係發夢，諗多定同嗰味嘢有關 ？ 最近仲好似嚴重咗，所以想上嚟分享 / 討論吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下真人真事分享 ：<br />\n<br />\n點解話最近嚴重咗呢？ 以前都偶然會發生，但最近頻密咗；訓覺嗰陣（一時時或突然之間），個頭突然會好重，好似頭痛/頭暈嗰種感覺但又唔係真係痛（sorry for 1999)... <br />\n<br />\n當依種&lsquo; 頭重 &rsquo; 嘅感覺維持5-10秒之後，如果我係盡早時間去控制返自己，就可以冇事醒返，郁到自己手手腳腳；但如果我唔理佢，由佢繼續keep住 &lsquo;頭重&rsquo; 狀態（頭重嗰刻好正，好似唔想比佢停咁），自己就會察覺到原來我訓著咗 / 進入咗夢境<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n進入咗狀態，我唔清楚係發夢 定 靈魂出竅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，然後遇到以下情況：<br />\n<br />\n第1次：冇頭重感覺，直接一醒郁唔到身，遠處見到有個白衣女人係床尾，然後佢用被單焗住我同掐我頸，最後我可以郁返，踢走張被單但昏睡咗，第二朝照鏡條頸紅唒。<br />\n<br />\n第2次： 有頭重感覺，夢見有個好惡嘅男人係一條走廊嘅遠處望住我，嚇到我即刻醒咗。<br />\n<br />\n第3次：頭重到個人都醒埋，郁唔到個身，feel到自己個嘴係咁講嘢，原來係有把男聲鬧緊我，好惡好兇狠，但原來把聲係嚟自我自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，即係有嘢上咗我身？基於本身有宗教信仰，聽到佢同我講嘅嘢係不停咁挑釁同試探你，眼望腳前方向見到有男影。<br />\n<br />\n第4次：有頭重感覺，醒咗，側訓緊郁唔到，聽到有人不停開我對門同閂門，驚到唔敢開眼；最尾忍唔住開眼，郁到隨即轉返平身訓，見到一大團黑影係我眼前飛嚟飛去，嚇一嚇醒，原來我仲側睡緊（有啲似夢中夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n第5次：有頭重感覺，見到自己穿過自己對門，沿大廳去阿媽房到，見阿媽同細佬訓得好甜；突然醒咗，即刻跑去阿媽間房搵阿媽，但得阿媽一個，原來細佬一早返咗學（發夢/諗多咗）<br />\n<br />\n第6+7次：有頭重感覺，平睡郁唔到，之後feel到比人扯低去訓，個頭由個枕頭跌落一格（即係好似比人捉住對腳扯低去，sorry for 1999 again) , 唔理再訓，再頭重，見到個無樣人係我面前出現，我係咁用腳踢佢，最後好似踢中佢，醒咗；發現自己冇被人扯落一格同埋好似冇踢過（因為如果有踢啲被單應該亂唒）<br />\n<br />\n夢境如幻如真，大家又有冇類似經歷？我都想知係咪得我會咁，我厭倦嗰種頭重而貌似撞嘢嘅感覺，好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遲吓再分享埋其他恐怖夢"},{"pid":"a69467dd2db13f8e78e8d4f634611eaa641bde70","tid":591016,"uid":116257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:18:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7624d62e28b409b13606d9469f14d0bb9877653","tid":591016,"uid":172840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:19:09.000Z","msg":"夢見樓主<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3dd3bbb5e4ca3051754bc8aa788b4db12fe2ef","tid":591016,"uid":116257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7624d62e28b409b13606d9469f14d0bb9877653","tid":591016,"uid":172840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:19:09.000Z","msg":"夢見樓主<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:21:33.000Z","msg":"但我唔恐怖啵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdfc161c20e0d8be267c84e90bcec59da63e9d3d","tid":591016,"uid":38790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:21:58.000Z","msg":"嘩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5b7c8b5ed8f7d064630731710ea49dba4f5ed4","tid":591016,"uid":173042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:22:17.000Z","msg":"我反而係好似由一個地方跌落一個地方。"},{"pid":"79d79bbfde66484d7c200618a8bdc69ba1af018d","tid":591016,"uid":116257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc5b7c8b5ed8f7d064630731710ea49dba4f5ed4","tid":591016,"uid":173042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:22:17.000Z","msg":"我反而係好似由一個地方跌落一個地方。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:25:25.000Z","msg":"依層我都試過，嗰種離心力又係好鬼真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"635c7f3ba42f04e5666ed56e767b61d37ac0d168","tid":591016,"uid":116257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdfc161c20e0d8be267c84e90bcec59da63e9d3d","tid":591016,"uid":38790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:21:58.000Z","msg":"嘩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:25:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7299f79db146e884c96d8d2e0a68cdc09f33612f","tid":591016,"uid":32354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:31:58.000Z","msg":"我覺得你要搵大師睇睇 似係俾野跟"},{"pid":"0949f642abcdbe3e95bb6951f9df260b0cc4face","tid":591016,"uid":57254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:44:35.000Z","msg":"唔洗問 唔係發夢<br />\n建議巴打搵師父做做法事"},{"pid":"94cd147664934eef6585290cb78cbf901382ded7","tid":591016,"uid":116257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:46:04.000Z","msg":"補充一吓：<br />\n<br />\n頭重完見到恐怖事情都係 喺我屋企發生。<br />\n<br />\n喺我工作地方同醫院都試過小睡時，有頭重發生，冇恐怖嘢見到，純見到自己仲訓緊但自己又張開咗眼周圍郁，聽到自己鼻鼾聲；問過同事佢地話唔見我有醒過，只聽到我鼻鼾聲。"},{"pid":"f6dc3a4201a42aaac4328f7af090a94cfbf0103f","tid":591016,"uid":116257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7299f79db146e884c96d8d2e0a68cdc09f33612f","tid":591016,"uid":32354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:31:58.000Z","msg":"我覺得你要搵大師睇睇 似係俾野跟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:46:50.000Z","msg":"某程度上我唔可以咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2ae6a14a68f2a4d4f860351c4d3e78a6f3cac8","tid":591016,"uid":116257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0949f642abcdbe3e95bb6951f9df260b0cc4face","tid":591016,"uid":57254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:44:35.000Z","msg":"唔洗問 唔係發夢<br />\n建議巴打搵師父做做法事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:48:09.000Z","msg":"我成日都說服自己可能發夢啫；唉，但我又忠於另一個信仰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1207aa1ead5d9b716d289ecf97b790a881ab2d7","tid":591016,"uid":16123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:50:38.000Z","msg":"反而成日發夢次次想返屋企，一係壞lift，一係有特發事，搞到次次都行樓梯返，但行極都行唔完，仲有好幾隻鬼追住我，未試過有一次係返到屋企"},{"pid":"d14b2797daf8d3e7bff95448cff943cea3e351fe","tid":591016,"uid":45627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:56:12.000Z","msg":"我唔係想挑戰樓主<br />\n但你都有懷疑係嗰味嘢<br />\n咁都唔係100%忠於你個信仰啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n既然係咁點解唔搵下其他方法去解決<br />\n好過依家連瞓覺都放鬆唔到"},{"pid":"f7c39bb665ee26d58bc512b4ca75409d9a9ff9f9","tid":591016,"uid":116257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1207aa1ead5d9b716d289ecf97b790a881ab2d7","tid":591016,"uid":16123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:50:38.000Z","msg":"反而成日發夢次次想返屋企，一係壞lift，一係有特發事，搞到次次都行樓梯返，但行極都行唔完，仲有好幾隻鬼追住我，未試過有一次係返到屋企"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:28:20.000Z","msg":"我未試過發重覆嘅夢"},{"pid":"b1fd34b82dce5277f780b7c34738927aa511ebed","tid":591016,"uid":133289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:33:26.000Z","msg":"你可以咁打<br />\n<br />\n第1-7：有頭重感覺"},{"pid":"df6bde9bd10727221814cf4a70b6722f520c01c5","tid":591016,"uid":116257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d14b2797daf8d3e7bff95448cff943cea3e351fe","tid":591016,"uid":45627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T07:56:12.000Z","msg":"我唔係想挑戰樓主<br />\n但你都有懷疑係嗰味嘢<br />\n咁都唔係100%忠於你個信仰啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n既然係咁點解唔搵下其他方法去解決<br />\n好過依家連瞓覺都放鬆唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:37:26.000Z","msg":"但某幾次郁返都係靠佢幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c74a913057898a93e117c4b109b3feb82070616b","tid":591016,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:40:05.000Z","msg":"耶撚?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ce8d6f19e0083dcba6831c37c495689f313a93","tid":591016,"uid":30950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:42:11.000Z","msg":"你唔信神既大能？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f93cb0216944097435f0e557b99dabe66f3c56","tid":591016,"uid":30950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:43:00.000Z","msg":"無論有咩事，主已預備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b386155f865d1886fe7b12fcb6131ae0be2c63e","tid":591016,"uid":116257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c74a913057898a93e117c4b109b3feb82070616b","tid":591016,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:40:05.000Z","msg":"耶撚?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:54:56.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但重點唔係依度"},{"pid":"c986e9f201711b4b6720860fb1c4327f0d4d16c0","tid":591016,"uid":116257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8f93cb0216944097435f0e557b99dabe66f3c56","tid":591016,"uid":30950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:43:00.000Z","msg":"無論有咩事，主已預備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:55:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2866773bbcbe7a5b4ed0897f616b951e6873f886","tid":591016,"uid":116257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T09:58:38.000Z","msg":"見冇咩人講，咁我講多個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有次發夢自己同個friend 無啦啦做咗救護定唔知消防，因為係夢入面我同佢企咗係一個火場入面，似係由交通意外而引起嘅一場大火；途中見到斷腳嘅，燒到&lsquo;窿&rsquo;唒嘅死人都有，真到連嗰陣烤肉味都聞到，但我從未見過死屍，自己又唔係做嗰啲行業，但真都咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"344822d14b208adc31fd27d373f4cc3a4f7f09da","tid":591016,"uid":37203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:08:53.000Z","msg":"夢過鍾馗教我捉鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}